  <h1 style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">Welcome</h1>
  <p>Welcome to the Department of Workforce Services (DWS) Eligibility Policy Manual for the Financial, Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP), and Child Care programs.</p>
  <h3 style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">DWS Mission</h3>
  <p>We strengthen Utah’s communities by connecting the workforce to new opportunities and providing services to individuals and families in need.</p>
  <h3 style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">DWS Vision</h3>
  <p>We are preparing our customer to prosper now and as the workforce of the future.</p>
  <h3 style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">DWS Code of Ethics</h3>
  <p>We are <span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;">accountable</span>.  This means we are</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;">Fair, considerate, and respectful in our interaction with our customers</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;">Committed to professional competence</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;">Honest and trustworthy in our relationships</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;">Truthful and accurate in what we say and write</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;">Law abiding in our activities</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;">Economical with our resources</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;">Committed to providing responsive and high-quality services</p>
  <h3 style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">DWS Cornerstones</h3>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Community Connection:</span> We engage with our partners to support opportunities for communities to prosper.</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Customer Experience:</span> We provide our customers with accessible, respectful and responsive service.</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Employee Success:</span> We promote a culture that fosters professional and personal fulfillment for our employees.</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Operational Excellence:</span> We deliver quality public service by implementing efficient solutions that are reliable and accurate</p>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
